<p class="govuk-body">Use this component when you're linking to a service that requires the user to sign in using Government Gateway.</p>


<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Where to place this component</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
You should place this component before the link to the service, unless there's a design pattern that says different.
</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
Force of law text should be put at the point the user needs to know it to complete their task.
</p>


<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Create it in Whitehall</h3>

